{"tid":945492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度烈火5號彈道飛彈第7度試射 射程涵蓋全中國","createTime":"2018-12-18T02:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T01:22:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9ab181f5d29d233534225877bd6eb0d39cba16","tid":945492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"印度今天成功在東部奧里薩省（Odisha）外海試射可攜帶核子彈頭的「烈火5號」洲際彈道飛彈，這是6年來的第7次試射。這款飛彈射程號稱達5000公里，可鎖定中國全境目標。<br />\n<br />\n印度Zee News報導，「烈火5號」（Agni-V）洲際彈道飛彈約下午1時30分在奧里薩省外海的卡蘭島（Dr Abdul Kalam Island）的綜合試驗場發射，這是「烈火5號」飛彈第7次試射。<br />\n<br />\n一名沒有具名的印度軍方人士告訴印度信通社（PTI），「烈火5號」下午的試射是由研發單位印度國防研究暨發展組織（DRDO）科學家所進行的用戶測試和戰略武力指揮。<br />\n<br />\nDRDO科學家指出，「烈火5號」被設計來精確擊中目標，由車載電腦引導，且輔以基於環式雷射陀螺（Ring Laser Gyro）的慣性導航系統（Inertial Navigation System）、微型慣性導航系統（Micro Inertial Navigation System）和全數位控制系統等，來達成精確擊中目標的任務。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，「烈火5號」具備更高的可靠性，更長的保存期限、更少的維護及更高的機動性。<br />\n<br />\n根據設計，全長17公尺的「烈火5號」，射程達5000公里，可攜帶1.5噸的核子彈頭，能直接攻擊中國領土的最北端，滿足印度軍方所有參數上的要求。<br />\n<br />\n在過去6次試射中，印度成功驗證了「烈火5號」可在非常短的準備時間下發射，及可從移動發射器發射等多項新技術。<br />\n<br />\n「烈火5號」從2012年開始進行試射，研發單位在第4次試射後曾一度樂觀地認為將可交付軍方使用，但可能在軍方還有要求下，又繼續試射且驗證新的技術，到今天已是第7次試射。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB5%E8%99%9F%E5%BD%88%E9%81%93%E9%A3%9B%E5%BD%88%E7%AC%AC7%E5%BA%A6%E8%A9%A6%E5%B0%84-%E5%B0%84%E7%A8%8B%E6%B6%B5%E8%93%8B%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-142125917.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%2583%2588%25E7%2581%25AB5%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2581%2593%25E9%25A3%259B%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%25AC%25AC7%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%25B0%2584-%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%25B6%25B5%25E8%2593%258B%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-142125917.html&d=LTtkzNEE4HXdLZFdqzpendr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bb12af51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB5%E8%99%9F%E5%BD%88%E9%81%93%E9%A3%9B%E5%BD%88%E7%AC%AC7%E5%BA%A6%E8%A9%A6%E5%B0%84-%E5%B0%84%E7%A8%8B%E6%B6%B5%E8%93%8B%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-142125917.html</a>"},{"pid":"7467df403d56393244fee75a0dac5cbd09c1d73e","tid":945492,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a42c1d7fd49632c4747f2ba8d27fd61a9583aca","tid":945492,"uid":15205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"口交部冇出嚟講兩句咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03bb8a67db1f6f1c91a876d558f8efba1305e70","tid":945492,"uid":222445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"印度有乜好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddad90db8932ba1530347adf62194618891c61e1","tid":945492,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5664f319d78884e4791757e6aa9a2f6a27064dad","tid":945492,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"開戰啦 等咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27823984a524c6a9ef5edb41a0bcc1489d809a15","tid":945492,"uid":67043,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"射導彈都好過互相掉石啦"},{"pid":"d532eb7236fc23bca1e305fc979f6f63d4cb75d0","tid":945492,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"講出黎都笑死 印度佬幾千年黎都係輸輸輸輸 點打呀"},{"pid":"7f3d8bb755f47624020b7462a7b29a729a535a13","tid":945492,"uid":71768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T